{"type": "article", "id": 53019, "title": "一款可拆卸清洗的烧烤架，便携又美观｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-09T23:22:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50097, "name": "Rcube"}, {"id": 50098, "name": "Curonian Deco"}, {"id": 50099, "name": "LaCividina"}, {"id": 50100, "name": "Mattice Boets"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}, {"id": 50101, "name": "Yuji Okitsu"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 19570, "name": "Constance Guisset"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180509224229kieBSmf0TA48aQJg.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 20.0px; font: 14.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Soave Seating by  Sebastian Herkner and Constance Guisset for LaCividina</h3><p>意大利家具品牌 LaCividina 在米兰设计周期间推出了两款新系列的软垫座椅，分别由德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 和法国设计师 Constance Guisset 设计。</p><p>Soave 座椅系列是 Sebastian Herkner 为 LaCividina 设计的第二个系列，包括扶手椅和沙发，大小不一，但座椅的深度都是一样的。弯曲的软垫元素呈现出亲切的椭圆造型，与细长的金属腿搭配，给人一种轻盈的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224417JD6b1XU0IFV24sOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224417vKlIf2UX6GWMEZiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224417XxZ8CIuVFKbYGzP1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224417WdFfrblUeozPOKDy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.285937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224417m6lfOZ7JM9bCBE3F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.125000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Constance Guisset 的 Wave 座椅，表现的是一系列自然景观，比如海浪或者岩石，可以模块化组合使用，也可以单独使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224436hqu3dYjZ7cDl1QR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224436hDvrC9uRIof8jGHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.797656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224436jAZ6zWDwlN1uxUGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224437v7Q9w65hfIVqa1lA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.950000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224437oK2UZWj8R3NIfzFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224437UiDGQeLnI09gTaqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.191406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Focus by Yuji Okitsu</h3><p>日本设计师 Yuji Okitsu 在米兰设计周上展示了名为 Focus 的装置作品，也是一组悬浮吊灯。他善于运用简单重复的单元，重新对光线进行深入的思考。</p><p>这是一个与周围环境相互作用的空间作品，以构建一个不断变化的感知空间。Focus 包括一些扁平的轻量级镜片，悬挂在天花板上。每一个灯又是放大镜，像是一颗颗巨型的水珠，为其所在的空间增添了无法停止的乐趣。</p><p>Yuji Okitsu 创造了一种新的观赏方式，通过聚焦和重新组合现有元素，例如光和空气，来回应空间中微妙的环境变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=l0648wv8fdy&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224507VqR32lPFJsoBEthL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.529340\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224507YWC9jFiOsSNKcwQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805092245079ClAwJ3d8tnsWBE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.146699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224507xEH7Z9hVq18FGdAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805092245082zFSh63gL7ZAOfni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545232\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050922450821nGBicbZYJH7IOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.498778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/yuji-okitsu-mobile-lenses-natural-light-interior-focus-05-09-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Curonian Tabletop Grill by Curonian Deco</h3><p>Curonian 桌面烧烤架的灵感源自北欧，由高质量的不锈钢制成，经久耐用，冬季、夏季都可以在户外使用。它不需要用户手动装配，收到货便是一个组装完整的烤架，可拆卸的底部方便清洗。</p><p>对于一个 4 至 8 人的小型烧烤派对，Curonian 是个理想的选择，它可以烤制食物 1 至 5 个小时，烤盘的大小一次性可以铺满 5 块鸡胸肉。不管是去自驾游还是野营，带上这个小巧、便携、方便清洗的烤架，都不会成为旅途中的负担。售价 249 美元，<a href=\"https://curonian.com/product/tabletop-grill/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224617yaSCRMZYhwqlz3Lc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735695\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050922461778mg16ER4ubftqjG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224617jMIQ1nBeKH8GA3as.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224618gFiC9wEcIJm83nlq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224618PGruevHBRYnJCLNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>VITRA Accessories Collection by Jasper Morrison</h3><p>瑞士家具大厂 VITRA 推出了一系列 VITRA 装饰配件系列，旨在创造一个充满生气的居住空间，通过新与旧、经典与现代的混搭而实现个性。英国设计师 Jasper Morrison，法国设计师兄弟 Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec，Hella Jongerius 以及 Michel Charlot 等明星设计团队，以经典的图形与作品为基础，描绘出一种美感、欢快与乐趣。</p><p>比如 Jasper Morrison 设计的托盘和高托盘，尽管第一眼看上去非常简单，但是色彩与尺寸的搭配，都是按照设计师“平常之极”的设计理念经过仔细推敲与研究的。</p><p>另有 Plate 餐桌，比例平衡，其细节通过不同位面与曲线之间的微妙互动呈现出来，展现出一种让人无法预料而又文雅精致的外形，同时这款桌子的设计能够与任何款式的椅子搭配在一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805092246452ecKfjbwAPauXqmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739609\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224645X3scSY4Jguo2QNWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224646SVuYkpDlqnaUd4cP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224645DSjOoeC2cTFKuAQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805092246465YxZqhePUvaWALCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/vitra-accessories-collection-jasper-morrison-05-04-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Reverse Clock by Mattice Boets</h3><p>Reverse 时钟，顾名思义，就是将人们对时针和分针的理解对调，沿外缘移动的是小小的时针，而从中点向四周延伸的，更长一些的是分针，容易让人产生错觉。设计简约，适合任何室内风格，将实用的细节变做设计的一部分，凸显设计师心思。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224726MiO3xSCc5NzeBPho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050922472630nZL58xASFRI2qW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224726RFE4fKT6saQqkL1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224727cgrkDEXCntfHUK8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050922472741rYSBTO5ERKCugF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224727OKHR63yzY9hb8dQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>RulerDock by Rcube</h3><p>RulerDock 是一个双方向的尺子，它支持所有苹果设备。它可以让你的 iPhone 水平或者垂直地坐在你的办公桌上，看起来简洁时尚，操刀其设计的是香港设计工作室 Rcube。</p><p>RulerDock 提供两个版本，15 厘米款和 20 厘米款，后者也适用于 iPad Pro，另配有一个 Apple Pen 的收纳槽，用来装饰书桌也不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805092247475xFN2md9hg1Dut0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224747UxhIvAgn5c1BHrSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224747nzCt3KgQSHflN2uy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224747fCX280YkMrV9Sl6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224747RvYdTCxqEMeLA2QB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180509224748nZA0Lfm4iUczEoFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}